Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.32,Default,Lady Runner,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.08,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good morning{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:35.19,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A cor do mar parece diferente...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:40.13,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Esta vista do Pacific Ocean é diferente\Nde tudo que eu vi na Inglaterra...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.94,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Eu realmente vim para o Japão!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.37,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A terra natal do meu father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:53.93,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Maio no Japão é quentinho como\Numa summer vacation, mamãe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:57.16,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Na Inglaterra, ainda estaria frio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:06.01,Default,Mayuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hora de acordar, Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:14.04,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Essa não... Aula de reforço...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:26.61,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Me desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:31.15,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No problem{\i0}. Por favor,\Nuse o {\i1}bathroom{\i0}, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.23,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Vista alguma coisa, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.82,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Mas estou usando uma toalha...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.09,Italics,Mayuko,0000,0000,0000,,Parece que as coisas estão bem\Nagitadas no segundo andar.
